{"number":102,"ayahs":[{"numberInSurah":1,"arabic":" أَلْهَىٰكُمُ ٱلتَّكَاثُرُ","translation":"Competition in [worldly] increase diverts you","transliteration":"Alhakumu attakathur","page":600},{"numberInSurah":2,"arabic":"حَتَّىٰ زُرْتُمُ ٱلْمَقَابِرَ","translation":"Until you visit the graveyards.","transliteration":"Hatta zurtumu almaqabir","page":600},{"numberInSurah":3,"arabic":"كَلَّا سَوْفَ تَعْلَمُونَ","translation":"No! You are going to know.","transliteration":"Kalla sawfa taAAlamoon","page":600},{"numberInSurah":4,"arabic":"ثُمَّ كَلَّا سَوْفَ تَعْلَمُونَ","translation":"Then, no! You are going to know.","transliteration":"Thumma kalla sawfa taAAlamoon","page":600},{"numberInSurah":5,"arabic":"كَلَّا لَوْ تَعْلَمُونَ عِلْمَ ٱلْيَقِينِ","translation":"No! If you only knew with knowledge of certainty...","transliteration":"Kalla law taAAlamoona AAilma alyaqeen","page":600},{"numberInSurah":6,"arabic":"لَتَرَوُنَّ ٱلْجَحِيمَ","translation":"You will surely see the Hellfire.","transliteration":"Latarawunna aljaheem","page":600},{"numberInSurah":7,"arabic":"ثُمَّ لَتَرَوُنَّهَا عَيْنَ ٱلْيَقِينِ","translation":"Then you will surely see it with the eye of certainty.","transliteration":"Thumma latarawunnaha AAayna alyaqeen","page":600},{"numberInSurah":8,"arabic":"ثُمَّ لَتُسْـَٔلُنَّ يَوْمَئِذٍ عَنِ ٱلنَّعِيمِ","translation":"Then you will surely be asked that Day about pleasure.","transliteration":"Thumma latus-alunna yawma-ithin AAaniannaAAeem","page":600}]}